essed, 0, fragmentLength);\\n        int cursor = fragmentLength;\\n        for (int readBytes = 0; (readBytes = in.read(compressed, cursor, compressed.length - cursor)) != -1;) {\\n            cursor += readBytes;\\n            if (cursor >= compressed.length) {\\n                byte[] newBuf = new byte[(compressed.length * 2)];\\n                System.arraycopy(compressed, 0, newBuf, 0, compressed.length);\\n                compressed = newBuf;\\n            }\\n        }\\n\\n[271 more lines in file. Use offset=121 to continue.]\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1782409830296}]}\n1914:[tool-call] delta {\"command\":\"rg \\\"uncompress\\\\(\\\" /home/mihailo/git/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/source_context/org.xerial.snappy/snappy-java/1.0.4.1/main/extracted/org/xerial/snappy/Snappy.java | head -30\"}\n1915:[tool-call] end id=call_2OyeDwhfYjUYMVdBnCzohHfK|fc_0b01435cdb5be1c0016a3d6a7454208193ac54aad1ca6a9000 name=bash args={\"command\": \"rg \\\"uncompress\\\\(\\\" /home/mihailo/git/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/source_context/org.xerial.snappy/snappy-java/1.0.4.1/main/extracted/org/xerial/snappy/Snappy.java | head -30\"}\n1916:[recv] {\"type\": \"message_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"thinking\", \"thinking\": \"\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0b01435cdb5be1c0016a3d6a67ecb0819380c95d12f366f4d3\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"content\\\":[],\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABqPWp0ZpxjUUsDLjkWj0U3iOSU6CPfxVsN7G6m0q99ExooO5DwkXqjEbzhxiVG68Sq78Y52svESYOZBrb-EnoyQ8N0qs4eDkTqtDhZH1QMVvMiKwSrJ2M4ajVbeb3xf2z2eI7qbjB1ghECJbO8335Zh1yEIPw0fZT4l43hdpzFq16_RHlkRQHTWpf46D9rYD_9jIs71ZvgfnBbH3WBXV7gqgM7kc_lXZoTq7z3iYMxW4uAQVGdQf4zX8xPCFw1IRpUhWjFZivhd2nD3JACrsuwysQWrD-aRTi2oouY5k8pbgnwjqune7mKwbdgBNlLEDi6SR7yTiXY86URYxS0VC8BgNGvuSJGmUcLLp9o7C2cHCM4lx4_xOFZ-58pY1n5EinT5cRnh2XHI3nzzCHX4hllJUo1wI2s9s4PNcn_GhOWSierb_iLzVmEp8NHUsa-M2-mu_funJ3s__9UpCh1udHaq5RaoB